JW6   *-----------------------------------------------------
 |    *  ADJUST FORD SHIP DATE TO SATURDAY
 |    *-----------------------------------------------------
 |   C           #FORD1    BEGSR
 |   C                     MOVE 'N'       UPDFLG  1
 |    * CHECK SUNDAY
 |   C                     MOVELBADEHZ    $DATE
 |   C                     CALL 'UTLR02'
 |   C                     PARM           $DATE   8
 |   C                     PARM           $DAY    2
 |   C                     PARM           $WEEK#  1
 |   C                     PARM           $RTN1   1
 |   C           $RTN1     IFEQ *BLANK
 |   C           $DAY      ANDNE'07'                       NOT SUNDAY
 |   C                     GOTO XFORD1
 |   C                     ENDIF
 |    * GET SATURDAY
 |   C                     MOVEL'-'       $SIGN   1
 |   C                     MOVEL'0001'    $DAYS   4
 |   C                     MOVEL'Y'       $IAF    1
 |   C                     CALL 'UTLR10'
 |   C                     PARM           $DATE   8
 |   C                     PARM           $SIGN   1
 |   C                     PARM           $DAYS   4
 |   C                     PARM           $IAF    1
 |   C                     PARM           $TGT8   8
 |   C                     PARM           $RTN2   1
 |   C           $RTN2     IFEQ *BLANK
 |   C                     MOVE 'Y'       UPDFLG
 |   C                     ENDIF
 |    *
JW6  C           XFORD1    ENDSR
